thor-ZRyB2U-4oqfhcjZ7xrf1_A">Nguyễn Du</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-t%E1%BA%B7ng-Vi-t%E1%BA%A3-th%E1%BB%ABa-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-nh%E1%BB%8B-th%E1%BA%ADp-nh%E1%BB%8B-v%E1%BA%ADn/poem-LHzRT_2tYsZxedOAYTvWlg">Phụng tặng Vi tả thừa trượng nhị thập nhị vận - 奉贈韋左丞丈二十二韻</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/Thi%E1%BB%87n-v%E1%BB%8B-chi%E1%BA%BFu/poem-7_zF-x1x1pienpNIOQCVKQ">Thiện vị chiếu - 禪位詔</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Khuy%E1%BA%BFt-danh-Vi%E1%BB%87t-Nam/author-kBTBt5Mbi6PPrH2sJkQAPw">Khuyết danh Việt Nam</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/Th%E1%BB%A7-07/poem-YCSk4JKFkKwU9wiU69vu6Q">Thủ 07 - 首０７</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%AA-H%E1%BB%AFu-Tr%C3%A1c/author-17RN7O2NKv8SmVJdOlpdFg">Lê Hữu Trác</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ACnh/Thu-d%E1%BA%A1-t%E1%BB%A9/poem-X-i9ytCIEVKcNIzxNr9wDA">Thu dạ tứ - 秋夜思</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C6%B0u-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-B%C3%ACnh/author-muwOXCdrb6me3mNm5PEtLQ">Lưu Phương Bình</a>)<br></div>	</div>
